Introduction to nano and vi/vim Text Editor 

# nano – Simple, beginner-friendly editor.
Example: nano mynotes.txt
Ctrl + O → Save (Write Out)
Ctrl + X → Exit
Ctrl + K → Cut a line

# vi / vim – Powerful editor (2 modes: command & insert).
Example: vi test.txt
Press i → Type something → Press Esc
Then type :wq to save and exit
